description:
Most people don’t want to hear the truth, especially when it hurts. But avoiding it won’t make life any easier. In this video, I lay out a set of brutal truths that can feel uncomfortable in the moment yet free you in the long run. The kind of honesty that forces you to rethink how you’re living, and why.
